case.title: Are there any single, hot caucasian guys left in this universe? - 30 (London)
case.text: Honestly, I don't know where you guys are but if by any chance you're online, between 29-37, have a thing for oriental women (there's only one of me so don't get your hopes up), financially stable and take care of your physique by working out regularly then I would like to hear from you.
